      "message": "I want this message to be named more specifically for a few reasons:\n\n- We don\u0027t want to add random fields to DeviceInfo (we should add them to api.HardwareFeatures instead). Nice to represent this in naming.\n- I\u0027m going to introduce DUTInfo message that contains all DUT system information messages (e.g. Features), which sounds similar to DeviceInfo.\n\nHow about naming it simply DeprecatedDeviceConfig? Then we can also keep using the same variable names, e.g. dc or deviceConfig, which reduces diff.",
